      <p>我是开源爱好者</p>
      <p>svn已经不用了，现在主要是git</p>
      <p>github帐号是 cod7ce </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="wrapper jumbotron text-center">
      <p>......</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="wrapper jumbotron">
      <p>记得联系我</p>
